#-    The Rise and Fall§0
§0of the Falaxian Empire  §0
§0Book 1: The Ylandóan War§0
§0Volume 2: The Invasion §0
§0The Ylandóans take a a city, and the Falaxians struggle to fight back, while discontent brews among the Ylandóans back home.
